We have implemented unit test cases inside the lambda/data-ingestion-pipeline/tests directory specifically for Aura QA1.

The objective of this setup is:

Whenever a new Aura QA1 file  is received in the tracer (prd-mmm-vendor-sync),
The pipeline should automatically pick up that file,
Execute the corresponding unit test cases against it,
Validate the data ingestion process.

This entire workflow will be fully automated through the CI/CD pipeline.
As part of CI execution, the tests will run automatically to ensure that any newly ingested Aura QA1 data meets the expected validation and quality checks.
